{"tid":2390180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2019區議會選舉咁多選舉呈請，聽日會有第一單判決","createTime":"2021-02-01T11:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T13:35:02.000Z","uid":153600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c58c1e42384d6513c9e686cf1e1635681482131","tid":2390180,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"◤是咁的 今日可能係我最後一日以翠屏區議員既身份服務街坊◢<br />\n<br />\n去年被落選人入稟要求選舉呈請，聽日高等法院就會頒布判詞，裁決究竟我係咪合法當選，輸左有機會要賠訟費，甚至唔講政府會唔會好似以前dq咁追返過去一年既辦事處開支，一切一切都要聽日下午3:00先會知。<br />\n<br />\n從來獨裁者都唔會放棄任何一個機會打壓群眾，大時代下每個人都承擔住唔同既責任，大家目標一致，無論結果點都好，希望大家都可以係咁黑暗既時代中揸緊信念。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20201020/s00001/1603178816541/區選落選建制派鄭強峰提選舉呈請稱遭抹黑-高院法官押後頒書面裁決\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20201020%2Fs00001%2F1603178816541%2F%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8%E8%90%BD%E9%81%B8%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E9%84%AD%E5%BC%B7%E5%B3%B0%E6%8F%90%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%91%88%E8%AB%8B%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%AD%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91-%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E9%A0%92%E6%9B%B8%E9%9D%A2%E8%A3%81%E6%B1%BA&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=9826d1d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20201020%2Fs00001%2F1603178816541%2F%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8%E8%90%BD%E9%81%B8%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E9%84%AD%E5%BC%B7%E5%B3%B0%E6%8F%90%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%91%88%E8%AB%8B%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%AD%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91-%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E9%A0%92%E6%9B%B8%E9%9D%A2%E8%A3%81%E6%B1%BA&h=407f82f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20201020/s00001/1603178816541/區選落選建制派鄭強峰提選舉呈請稱遭抹黑-高院法官押後頒書面裁決</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n翠屏辦公室：翠屏南邨翠櫻樓地下5室<br />\n開放時間：星期一至五上午10時至6時<